  <brief_title>Target Volume in Noninvasive Positive Pressure Ventilation</brief_title>
  <acronym>CIBLE</acronym>
  <official_title>Comparison of Two Noninvasive Positive Pressure Ventilation Devices Using Target Volume Modes in Obesity Hypoventilation Syndrome (OHS): A Pilot Randomized Crossover Controlled Trial</official_title>
